<template>
    {{ this.$route.params.id }}
</template>

<script>
    import { useRoute } from 'vue-router';

    export default{
        name: "ViewListing",
        data(){
            return{
                listing:Object
            }
        },
        methods:{
            async fetchListing(){
                const res = await fetch("http://localhost:1337/api/listings/"+this.$route.params.id )

                this.listing = await res.json();

                console.log("listing", this.listing)
            }
        },
        async created(){
            const res = await this.fetchListing();
        },
    }
</script>
